{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id0e2b90ad-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7231c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"7231c"},"text":"§ 7231c.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Eligibility","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"A local educational agency, or consortium of such agencies where appropriate, is eligible to receive a grant under this part to carry out the purpose of this part if such agency or consortium—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e2b90ae-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7231c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" is implementing a plan undertaken pursuant to a final order issued by a court of the United States, or a court of any State, or any other State agency or official of competent jurisdiction, that requires the desegregation of minority-group-segregated children or faculty in the elementary schools and secondary schools of such agency; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e2b90af-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7231c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" without having been required to do so, has adopted and is implementing, or will, if a grant is awarded to such local educational agency, or consortium of such agencies, under this part, adopt and implement a plan that has been approved by the Secretary as adequate under title VI of the Civil Rights Act of 1964 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s2000d"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 2000d","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] for the desegregation of minority-group-segregated children or faculty in such schools."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id0e2b90b0-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/10/tIV/s4404"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–10, title IV, § 4404","children":[],"tail":", formerly title V, § 5304, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/110/tV/s501"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–110, title V, § 501","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-01-08"},"text":"Jan. 8, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/115/1807"},"text":"115 Stat. 1807","children":[],"tail":"; renumbered title IV, § 4404, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/95/tIV/s4001/b/3/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–95, title IV, § 4001(b)(3)(A)","children":[],"tail":", (B), (D)(i), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-12-10"},"text":"Dec. 10, 2015","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/129/1967"},"text":"129 Stat. 1967","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id0e2b90b1-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id0e2b90b2-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id0e2b90b3-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Civil Rights Act of 1964, referred to in par. (2), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/352"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–352","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1964-07-02"},"text":"July 2, 1964","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/78/241"},"text":"78 Stat. 241","children":[],"tail":". Title VI of the Act is classified generally to subchapter V (§ 2000d et seq.) of chapter 21 of Title 42, The Public Health and Welfare. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s2000a"},"text":"section 2000a of Title 42","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"id0e2b90b4-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/10/s4404"},"text":"section 4404 of Pub. L. 89–10","children":[],"tail":" was classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s3124"},"text":"section 3124 of this title","children":[],"tail":", prior to the general amendment of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/10"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–10","children":[],"tail":" by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/382"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–382","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
